    strengths: "Well-rounded private hospital with 150+ beds and 40 full-time physicians plus 200 rotating specialists. Strong multilingual support — dedicated medical translators fluent in English, Japanese, Filipino, and Korean available on weekdays, many with clinical backgrounds (EKG technicians, RNs). Comprehensive specialty coverage including orthopedics, minimally invasive surgery, and dialysis. More affordable than Bangkok Hospital or Chiang Mai Ram while maintaining international standards. Partnership agreements with major four- and five-star hotels and corporations. Good insurance claims assistance department. Central city location with upscale inpatient rooms featuring river/mountain views, kitchens, and balconies. 24-hour emergency.",
